較低的FFP1都比不上。荷蘭衛生單位發現中國口罩不符合標準後，立刻停止分發給醫院且展開回收。<br />\n<br />\n對此，中國官媒《環球時報》採訪中國相關單位表示，斥責西方媒體將國際防疫轉為政治化，「中國廠商加班供應外國需求，本身出發點是善意的，不應將物資品質問題政治化，破壞疫情國際合作的效果。」再進一步委婉表示，中國的口罩確實有些不合標準，因為「臨時趕訂單，又很難與買方進行有效溝通，出現規格和品質不對接的情況在所難免」。對此，中國網友在底下留言「我們4.2萬醫護都沒問題，到了歐洲就事多」、「所以說現在捐東西要謹慎，都是些白眼狼」、「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中國生產肯定按中國標準</span></strong>，荷蘭非要按歐盟標準」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/03/30/2480174-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F03%2F30%2F2480174-XXL.jpg&h=f121bb82&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T10:32:08.000Z","msg":"4.2萬醫護當中好似死既病既都唔少"},{"pid":"2d8be0b3d237354edeb5996222997e43cc230b64","tid":1950351,"uid":2424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T10:33:05.000Z","msg":"呢單案既重點係 浪子回頭金不換！"},{"pid":"83166130ffdf519e7bd45323ea406d02ab207506","tid":1950351,"uid":325023,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T10:33:15.000Z","msg":"支那口罩廠員工用口罩抹鞋再拎去出口<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SalihHudayar/status/1244417505931808773?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSalihHudayar%2Fstatus%2F1244417505931808773%3Fs%3D20&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2Vtn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=eb92fdbd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSalihHudayar%2Fstatus%2F1244417505931808773%3Fs%3D20&h=04929e25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SalihHudayar/status/1244417505931808773?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"82eb28e53f029c7eb292df5f841a6c93d228bb9f","tid":1950351,"uid":158457,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T10:35:55.000Z","msg":"唔合規格仲點用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n彈回頭都可以話係政治問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明係自己錯都可以屈鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i